name: Daring Delight Jar
description:
Daring Delight is a multi-use glass jar able to serve a couple of different functions.  This jar can be a part of your décor by holding freshly cut flowers or store various items while still looking stylish.  

The green and white background is a cotton material from a beach-themed shirt.  The pink, yellow, and orange ribbon help correlate with the orange felt flower with matching orange bead to make a bold statement against the background.  Add a little bit of beach chic to your home.

Don’t miss you chance to decorate your home with this beautiful jar.
